<div class="l-constrained">
  <article>
    <div class="l-campaign__content l-campaign__content--padded-top">
      <%= heading_tag 'Paying too much tax on savings?', class: 'l-campaign__heading', level: 1 %>
      <p>
        Individual Savings Accounts (ISAs) are a tax-efficient way of saving money. There are two types of ISAs: Cash ISAs and Stocks and Shares ISAs.
      </p>
      <p>
        <b>Cash ISAs</b> allow you to earn interest on your savings, tax free and work in much the same way as a normal savings account.
      </p>
      <p>
        <b>Stocks and Shares ISAs</b> allow your investment to grow free of any Capital Gains tax liability.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href="/en/news/two-in-five-have-never-paid-into-a-cash-isa">Are you one of the millions missing out on tax-free saving?</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="/en/users/sign_up">Register on our website to receive an ISA alert.</a>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <div class="callout">
        <%= heading_tag 'Who is MA anyway?', level: 3 %>
        <p>
          Weâ€™re the Money Advice Service, an independent service set up by government to help people like you make the most of your money.
        </p>
        <p>
          We give free, unbiased money advice online, on webchat, over the phone, in printed guides and face to face.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="l-campaign__next-steps">
      <%= heading_tag 'Next steps', class: 'l-campaign__next-steps-heading', level: 2 %>

      <div class="next-step">
        <a class="next-step__link" href="/en/articles/price-comparison-sites-guide">
          <%= heading_tag 'Comparison sites', level: 2, class: 'next-step__heading' %>
          <p class="next-step__content">
            Use comparison websites to weigh up different options and help you find out what might be best for your money.
          </p>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="next-step">
        <a class="next-step__link" href="/en/articles/cash-isas">
          <%= heading_tag 'Cash ISAs', level: 2, class: 'next-step__heading' %>
          <p class="next-step__content">
            Cash ISAs are savings accounts that pay tax-free interest, but with an upper limit on what you can save each year.
          </p>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="next-step">
        <a class="next-step__link" href="/en/articles/stocks-and-shares-isas">
          <%= heading_tag 'Stocks & Shares ISAs', level: 2, class: 'next-step__heading' %>
          <p class="next-step__content">
            A Stocks and Shares ISA can contain a range of different investment products to help save you tax.
          </p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
</div>

